{"tid":1281482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"G20眾籌係班無腦既先會做（長文）","createTime":"2019-07-03T09:53:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T22:37:14.000Z","uid":96799,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"154c8eb6603f3279be001d369992aa114eaf9b8e","tid":1281482,"uid":96799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:53:33.000Z","msg":"唔好負評住<br />\n<br />\n我同你地見到標題一樣咁火滾<br />\n因為今朝我啲藍屍親戚就係send咗呢段文比我：<a href=\"https://www.silentmajority.hk/articles/1003144?fbclid=IwAR1sVs3ZASk_t839M7dcdzjKymd-D21T__LOceeqOJ63ci8p1hRfG5e5gZc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.silentmajority.hk%2Farticles%2F1003144%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1sVs3ZASk_t839M7dcdzjKymd-D21T__LOceeqOJ63ci8p1hRfG5e5gZc&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaVytC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=c43965a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.silentmajority.hk/articles/1003144?fbclid=IwAR1sVs3ZASk_t839M7dcdzjKymd-D21T__LOceeqOJ63ci8p1hRfG5e5gZc</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然係藍屍文，但係其實我地都無辦法否認，今日或將來西方勢力會幫我地，都係源自對自己國家既利益。<br />\n<br />\n再黎睇下我啲親戚點回：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/azWykvw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FazWykvw.jpg&h=0560c281&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G7GndQx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG7GndQx.jpg&h=8f099ac5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XpmndQy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXpmndQy.jpg&h=417db6ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實佢地成班已經係個group偏激左好耐<br />\n重點係佢地都係出國讀過書 屋企有錢個班<br />\n呢一班人唔係好似啲廢中廢老咁<br />\nsend啲長輩圖就搞得掂<br />\n<br />\n而且反送中都搞左差唔多成個月<br />\n除非有翻天覆地既事發生 唔係大致上個班<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有學識既中年</span></strong>已經定曬立場 好難改變<br />\n<br />\n既然香港入面已經做得差唔多<br />\n外國又成日淨係打嘴炮甚至一有暴力就轉曬呔<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地係時候改變策略 打入對方陣營！！！！！</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n先由<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">派傳單</span></span></strong>比自由行開始<br />\n無需非常偏激！<br />\n否則就會令佢地維護自己地方既心態出黎！<br />\n主要目的只係<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">啓發民智</span></span></strong>！！！點到即止！引人反思！<br />\n<br />\n就好似好多大陸人過左福田口岸個關<br />\n都會驚歎只隔一條河<br />\n香港居然可以貼滿吹捧法輪功既banner<br />\n頓覺香港同大陸言論自由既差別！<br />\n<br />\n其實大陸已經有覺醒既人！<br />\n比如最近廣東因為要起垃圾焚燒場 都有好多人抗議<br />\n一開始又係比啲狗打 細路都打！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CLkCNhF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCLkCNhF.jpg&h=d101268f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=hZ6T3dPyMXY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhZ6T3dPyMXY&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaVytC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=128e103b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=hZ6T3dPyMXY</a><br />\n係咪似曾相識呢<br />\n<br />\n亦有廣州維權人士支持佔中九子<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190428/59540716\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190428%2F59540716&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaVytC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=32c2fd4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190428%2F59540716&h=dba78117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190428/59540716</a><br />\n<br />\n既然目標一致既都係兄弟<br />\n我地既不分化不割席應該係要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">擴大</span></strong>到敵方<br />\n先更大機會獲勝！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我地要開啟民智<br />\n並搵出已醒覺既中國人出黎<br />\n一齊爬山！！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟知識有限 <br />\n各位巴絲 尤其文宣組 傳單內容我地一齊諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e7bbb227d0aae5f02ca69e609b62eda95ef6052","tid":1281482,"uid":28279,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:57:56.000Z","msg":"班人無得救，你講送中條例會以言入罪拉人去大陸屈打成招，佢只會話你作大，罪犯先會送中<br />\n完全無視現實好多冤獄，總之佢自己無事就話你作大講大話"},{"pid":"5bd9d4f9d0caf8cdecaac7d45e7d880e05314a11","tid":1281482,"uid":96799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e7bbb227d0aae5f02ca69e609b62eda95ef6052","tid":1281482,"uid":28279,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:57:56.000Z","msg":"班人無得救，你講送中條例會以言入罪拉人去大陸屈打成招，佢只會話你作大，罪犯先會送中<br />\n完全無視現實好多冤獄，總之佢自己無事就話你作大講大話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:06:48.000Z","msg":"除左自私無其他原因"},{"pid":"1e01c88867a431d17d68bcccd9967404728dd3e5","tid":1281482,"uid":96799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:07:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"191923638446773c1ecbbbc973fe5af667707ff4","tid":1281482,"uid":119478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:12:39.000Z","msg":"訴諸權威有無用？<br />\n讀過下書既人通常都會認同專業人士<br />\nQuote近排各行各業既聯署聲明"},{"pid":"9055c99680a672c890e0947ed8af6bc3058024a0","tid":1281482,"uid":258480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:20:46.000Z","msg":"高質。推"},{"pid":"1b8591090f9a301b4ec9f7f47e73479482760cbe","tid":1281482,"uid":96799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:50:54.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"bb81892ad1c9324bcf94e9eebe9004a2e49c63f2","tid":1281482,"uid":96799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:14:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c70eb6b78b4aa0704f4be8f9806277b955a91d55","tid":1281482,"uid":56954,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:29:02.000Z","msg":"屌講起就嬲<br />\n人地中國政府都識得回應市民<br />\n你香港呢<br />\n連中國政府都不如<br />\n中國殖民地走狗既極致"},{"pid":"fdf14ea2b66ecd06ce1184b58a68d64457a58bb7","tid":1281482,"uid":96799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T21:08:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1275934/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1275934/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n佢地越驚 我地越要做<br />\n推！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"320b78b362c9a926a12e1341e755fe8944601cbf","tid":1281482,"uid":96799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T21:08:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"efa6bc9556266f32552a75b0f491c7bf49e99fc7","tid":1281482,"uid":134751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T22:17:59.000Z","msg":"其實唔係好明篇文係乜point 純屌美國係壞人？壞係邊到又好似冇解釋 屌睇到我皺哂眉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b159e2fe05f7141455852497291f1e549f9bb7","tid":1281482,"uid":23061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T22:28:57.000Z","msg":"好簡單<br />\n我諗好多人都寧願益9外國都唔撚益冇一個係無辜嘅 支 拿 人"},{"pid":"dd82e943d092878e25d0e40c2e1428646a1ca545","tid":1281482,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efa6bc9556266f32552a75b0f491c7bf49e99fc7","tid":1281482,"uid":134751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T22:17:59.000Z","msg":"其實唔係好明篇文係乜point 純屌美國係壞人？壞係邊到又好似冇解釋 屌睇到我皺哂眉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T22:29:52.000Z","msg":"港人港地d廢文係咁<br />\n打一大段野就以為自己好有道理，實質都係幫中國含"},{"pid":"ca17a2de92a614f272da793c8ef959e622abf361","tid":1281482,"uid":32391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T22:37:14.000Z","msg":"重點係佢地都係出國讀過書 屋企有錢個班<br />\n<br />\n即係佢地係現有制度既得利益者<br />\n現代貴族 你同佢地講d人無飯食 佢地只會答你點解唔食蛋糕<br />\n其實唔需要同佢地講咁多"}]}